Symbol.Script_3D:
! Square Louver Face Ceiling Diffuser
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
CALL "MEP_m_RequestSystemGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL returned_parameters gs_cont_pen, sMat
IF useSysMat AND MEP_StrConnectionData[1][2] <> "0" THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- TRANSFORMATION --- !
XFORM MEP_Position[2][1], MEP_Position[3][1], dZx, MEP_Position[1][1], MEP_Position[2][2], MEP_Position[3][2], dZy, MEP_Position[1][2], MEP_Position[2][3], MEP_Position[3][3], dZz, MEP_Position[1][3]
! --- MAIN BOX + LOUVERS --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN PRISM_ 10, edgeHeight, prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 15, -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 15, -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 15, prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 15, prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, -1, prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, -prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth, -prismInsideHalfDepth, 15, prismInsideHalfWidth, prismInsideHalfDepth, -1
ADDz edgeHeight ROTz 90 ROTy -90
DIM StraightPosition[3][3] StraightPosition[1][1] = 0 StraightPosition[1][2] = 0 StraightPosition[1][3] = 0
StraightPosition[2][1] = 1 StraightPosition[2][2] = 0 StraightPosition[2][3] = 0
StraightPosition[3][1] = 0 StraightPosition[3][2] = 1 StraightPosition[3][3] = 0
DIM ConnectionData[2][26]
FOR i = 1 TO 2 FOR j = 1 TO 26 ConnectionData[i][j] = 0 NEXT j NEXT i
ConnectionData[1][12] = A ConnectionData[1][13] = B ConnectionData[1][21] = 1
ConnectionData[2][12] = ConWidth_1+ConWallThickness_1*2 ConnectionData[2][13] = ConDepth_1+ConWallThickness_1*2 ConnectionData[2][21] = MEP_NumConnectionData[1][21]
CALL "MEP_m_Duct_4" PARAMETERS MEP_Position = StraightPosition, MEP_NumberConnections = 2, MEP_NumConnectionData = ConnectionData, MEP_StraightLength = ZZYZX-edgeHeight, duct_show = 1, showHtps = 0, gs_DuctMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen DEL 3
ang = 0 IF A < B THEN A_temp = A A = B B = A_temp
ang = 90 ENDIF
ROTz ang divThick = (B-edgeThick*2)/12 louverThick = divThick-0.003 IF ABS(MEP_NumConnectionData[1][21] - 1) < EPS THEN dist = MAX((A-ConWidth_1-ConWallThickness_1*2)/2,(B-ConDepth_1-ConWallThickness_1*2)/2) IF ABS(MEP_NumConnectionData[1][21] - 2) < EPS THEN dist = MAX((A-ConWidth_1-ConWallThickness_1*2)/2,(B-ConWidth_1-ConWallThickness_1*2)/2) height = edgeHeight + ((ZZYZX-edgeHeight)/dist)*(edgeThick+divThick+louverThick) ruledLHeight = 0.04 IF (ruledLHeight-height) > -EPS THEN ruledLHeight = height-0.001 ruledLHalfWidth = A/2-edgeThick-divThick*5 ruledLHalfDepth = divThick ruledLInsideHalfWidth = ruledLHalfWidth-divThick
RULED 4, 1+2+4+16+32, ruledLHalfWidth, ruledLHalfDepth, 0, -ruledLHalfWidth, ruledLHalfDepth, 0, -ruledLHalfWidth, -ruledLHalfDepth, 0, ruledLHalfWidth, -ruledLHalfDepth, 0,
ruledLInsideHalfWidth, 0, ruledLHeight, -ruledLInsideHalfWidth, 0, ruledLHeight, -ruledLInsideHalfWidth, 0, ruledLHeight, ruledLInsideHalfWidth, 0, ruledLHeight
FOR i = 1 TO 4 ruledLHalfWidth = ruledLHalfWidth+divThick ruledLHalfDepth = ruledLHalfDepth+divThick ruledLInsideHalfWidth = ruledLHalfWidth-louverThick ruledLInsideHalfDepth = ruledLHalfDepth-louverThick
RULED 4, 4+16+32, ruledLHalfWidth, ruledLHalfDepth, 0, -ruledLHalfWidth, ruledLHalfDepth, 0, -ruledLHalfWidth, -ruledLHalfDepth, 0, ruledLHalfWidth, -ruledLHalfDepth, 0,
ruledLInsideHalfWidth, ruledLInsideHalfDepth, ruledLHeight, -ruledLInsideHalfWidth, ruledLInsideHalfDepth, ruledLHeight, -ruledLInsideHalfWidth, -ruledLInsideHalfDepth, ruledLHeight, ruledLInsideHalfWidth, -ruledLInsideHalfDepth, ruledLHeight NEXT i DEL 1 ELSE PRISM_ 5, ZZYZX, prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 15, -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 15, -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 15, prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 15, prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, -1 ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1
DEL TOP
END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Square Louver Face Ceiling Diffuser
CALL "MEP_m_RequestPlanViewGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL returned_parameters gs_symbtype_2D_m CALL "MEP_m_RequestSystemGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL returned_parameters gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
HptsUnIDBeginForConnEnds = 30000
hceID_1 = HptsUnIDBeginForConnEnds+100 call "2dmacro" parameters all, type_symb = 1 if show_axis then hotspot2 0,0 end endif unID = 1 IF ABS(dZz-1) < EPS THEN ADD2 MEP_Position[1][1], MEP_Position[1][2] ROT2 dirAngOnXYPlane
HOTSPOT2 prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, unID: unID=unID+1
IF gs_symbtype_2D_m = 1 OR gs_symbtype_2D_m = 2 THEN ! Realistic, Electric PUT prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 1, -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 1, -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 1, prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 1, prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, -1
POLY2_B NSP/3, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen,
GET (NSP)
IF ABS(MEP_NumConnectionData[1][21] - 1) < EPS THEN LINE2 prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, (ConWidth_1+ConWallThickness_1*2)/2, (ConDepth_1+ConWallThickness_1*2)/2 LINE2 prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, (ConWidth_1+ConWallThickness_1*2)/2, (-ConDepth_1+ConWallThickness_1*2)/2 LINE2 -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, (-ConWidth_1+ConWallThickness_1*2)/2, (-ConDepth_1+ConWallThickness_1*2)/2 LINE2 -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, (-ConWidth_1+ConWallThickness_1*2)/2, (ConDepth_1+ConWallThickness_1*2)/2 ENDIF ENDIF
IF gs_symbtype_2D_m = 3 THEN ! RCP HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
LINE2 prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth LINE2 0, 0, prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth RECT2 prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth END ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = 1, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1 = ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 0 DEL 2 ELSE
HOTSPOT2 outCoords[4][1], outCoords[4][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[5][1], outCoords[5][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[6][1], outCoords[6][2], unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 outCoords[7][1], outCoords[7][2], unID: unID=unID+1
HOTSPOT2 outCoords[1][1], outCoords[1][2], hceID_1
SET FILL gs_fill_type
PEN gs_cont_pen IF gs_fill_pen THEN PEN gs_fill_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 3+32, 4, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 PEN gs_cont_pen PROJECT2{3} 3, 270, 2, 8, 0, 0, 0, 0, PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ENDIF
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
type_symb = 1 success = LIBRARYGLOBAL ("Libraryflobals-mep", "show_axis", show_axis) ! Square Louver Face Ceiling Diffuser
EPS = 0.0001
! --- HARDCODED AND DERIVED VARIABLES --- !
edgeThick = 0.025 edgeHeight = 0.015 IF A < edgeThick*4+0.001 THEN A = edgeThick*4+0.001 IF B < edgeThick*4+0.001 THEN B = edgeThick*4+0.001
prismHalfWidth = A/2 prismHalfDepth = B/2 prismInsideHalfWidth = prismHalfWidth-edgeThick prismInsideHalfDepth = prismHalfDepth-edgeThick
! ---------------- ! ! --- Z vector --- ! ! ---------------- !
dZx = -MEP_Position[3][2]*MEP_Position[2][3]+MEP_Position[3][3]*MEP_Position[2][2] dZy = -MEP_Position[3][3]*MEP_Position[2][1]+MEP_Position[3][1]*MEP_Position[2][3] dZz = -MEP_Position[3][1]*MEP_Position[2][2]+MEP_Position[3][2]*MEP_Position[2][1]
! --- dirAngOnXYPlane of the route --- !
IF ABS(dZz-1) < EPS THEN arCosVal = MEP_Position[3][1]/1 IF ABS(arCosVal) > 1 AND SGN(arCosVal) = -1 THEN arCosVal = -1 IF ABS(arCosVal) > 1 AND SGN(arCosVal) = 1 THEN arCosVal = 1 dirAngOnXYPlane = ACS(arCosVal)-90 IF SGN(MEP_Position[3][2]) = -1 THEN dirAngOnXYPlane = 180-dirAngOnXYPlane ENDIF
!!! +++ Transformational Matrix +++ !!!
DIM tMatrix[3][3]
tMatrix[1][1] = MEP_Position[2][1] tMatrix[1][2] = MEP_Position[2][2] tMatrix[1][3] = MEP_Position[2][3]
tMatrix[2][1] = MEP_Position[3][1] tMatrix[2][2] = MEP_Position[3][2] tMatrix[2][3] = MEP_Position[3][3]
tMatrix[3][1] = dZx tMatrix[3][2] = dZy tMatrix[3][3] = dZz
!!! +++ Input Coordinates +++ !!!
PUT ConPosX_1+gs_Connections[1][4]*ConLength_1, ConPosY_1+gs_Connections[1][5]*ConLength_1, ConPosZ_1+gs_Connections[1][6]*ConLength_1 PUT gs_Connections[1][4], gs_Connections[1][5], gs_Connections[1][6] PUT gs_Connections[1][7], gs_Connections[1][8], gs_Connections[1][9]
PUT prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 0 PUT -prismHalfWidth, prismHalfDepth, 0 PUT -prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 0 PUT prismHalfWidth, -prismHalfDepth, 0
Coordinates = NSP/3
DIM inCoords[20][3]
FOR cnum = 1 TO Coordinates inCoords[cnum][1] = GET(1) inCoords[cnum][2] = GET(1) inCoords[cnum][3] = GET(1) NEXT cnum
! --- the Matrix Operation, what make the Output-Coordinates
DIM outCoords[20][3]
FOR cnum = 1 TO Coordinates outCoords[cnum][1] = inCoords[cnum][1]*tMatrix[1][1]+inCoords[cnum][2]*tMatrix[2][1]+inCoords[cnum][3]*tMatrix[3][1]+MEP_Position[1][1] outCoords[cnum][2] = inCoords[cnum][1]*tMatrix[1][2]+inCoords[cnum][2]*tMatrix[2][2]+inCoords[cnum][3]*tMatrix[3][2]+MEP_Position[1][2] outCoords[cnum][3] = inCoords[cnum][1]*tMatrix[1][3]+inCoords[cnum][2]*tMatrix[2][3]+inCoords[cnum][3]*tMatrix[3][3]+MEP_Position[1][3] NEXT cnum
z = MEP_Position[1][3]
PARAMETERS ac_toplevel = z PARAMETERS ac_bottomlevel = z

Symbol.Script_VL:
call "2dmacro" parameters all, type_symb = type_symb ! Square Louver Face Ceiling Diffuser
CALL "MEP_m_RequestPlanViewGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL returned_parameters gs_symbtype_2D_m
call "FM_types_MEP" parameters
DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 1 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
IF useSysMat AND MEP_StrConnectionData[1][2] <> "0" THEN LOCK "MainBoxMaterial" IF MEP_StrConnectionData[1][2] = "0" THEN LOCK "useSysMat"
! --- MAIN PARAMETERS --- !
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF ZZYZX < edgeHeight*2 THEN ZZYZX = edgeHeight*2 PARAMETERS ZZYZX = ZZYZX ENDIF VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [edgeHeight*2,]
IF A < edgeThick*4+0.001 THEN A = edgeThick*4+0.001 PARAMETERS A = A ENDIF VALUES "A" RANGE [edgeThick*4+0.001,]
IF B < edgeThick*4+0.001 THEN B = edgeThick*4+0.001 PARAMETERS B = B ENDIF VALUES "B" RANGE [edgeThick*4+0.001,] ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
PARAMETERS MEP_NumberConnections = 1
! --- THE ONLY CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 1 ConName = `Соединение Конца Воздуховода`
ConDVecX = 0 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = 1
ConWVecX = 1 ConWVecY = 0 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF ABS(MEP_NumConnectionData[1][21] - 2) < EPS THEN VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE (0, MIN(A-0.001-ConWallThickness_1*2,B-0.001-ConWallThickness_1*2)] PARAMETERS ConDepth_1 = ConWidth_1 HIDEPARAMETER "ConDepth_1" ELSE IF ConWidth_1 > A-0.001-ConWallThickness_1*2 THEN ConWidth_1 = A-0.001-ConWallThickness_1*2 PARAMETERS ConWidth_1 = ConWidth_1 ENDIF VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE (0, A-0.001-ConWallThickness_1*2]
IF ConDepth_1 > B-0.001-ConWallThickness_1*2 THEN ConDepth_1 = B-0.001-ConWallThickness_1*2 PARAMETERS ConDepth_1 = ConDepth_1 ENDIF VALUES "ConDepth_1" RANGE (0, B-0.001-ConWallThickness_1*2] ENDIF
VALUES "ConWallThickness_1" RANGE [0, MIN((A-0.001-ConWidth_1)/2, (B-0.001-ConDepth_1)/2)]
PARAMETERS ConPosX_1 = 0 PARAMETERS ConPosY_1 = 0 PARAMETERS ConPosZ_1 = ZZYZX ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_1, ConPosY = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_1, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
IF SetProgram THEN SetProgram = 0 PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram ENDIF
FOR k = 1 TO MEP_NumberConnections FOR i = 1 TO 9 j = 1+INT((i-0.5)/3) MEP_NumConnectionData[k][i] = outCoords[j+3*(k-1)][i-3*(j-1)] PARAMETERS MEP_NumConnectionData[k][i] = MEP_NumConnectionData[k][i] NEXT i NEXT k
